<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Porsche Panamera Guide</title>
  <style>
    /* General Styles */
body {
  font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2c2c2c, #1a1a1a); /* Dark grey gradient */
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  color: #fff; /* White text for contrast */
}

.container {
  max-width: 1000px;
  margin: 20px auto;
  padding: 20px;
  background: #2c2c2c; /* Dark grey background */
  box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.3); /* Golden shadow */
  border-radius: 10px;
}

h1, h2 {
  color: #ffd700; /* Golden color for headings */
}

h1 {
  text-align: center;
  font-size: 2.5rem;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
}

h2 {
  font-size: 1.8rem;
  margin-top: 30px;
  margin-bottom: 15px;
  padding-bottom: 10px;
  border-bottom: 3px solid #ffd700; /* Golden border */
  display: inline-block;
}

p, ul {
  line-height: 1.8;
  font-size: 1rem;
  color: #ddd; /* Light grey for readability */
}

ul {
  list-style-type: disc;
  padding-left: 20px;
}

li {
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}

/* Card Styles */
.card {
  background: #3a3a3a; /* Medium grey */
  border-radius: 10px;
  box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.2); /* Golden shadow */
  padding: 20px;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
}

.card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-5px);
  box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.4); /* Brighter golden shadow on hover */
}

/* Images Section */
.images {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  margin: 20px 0;
}

.images img {
  max-width: 100%; /* Ensures the image fits the container width */
  height: auto; /* Maintains aspect ratio */
  border-radius: 10px;
  box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.3); /* Golden shadow */
  transition: transform 0.3s ease;
}

.images img:hover {
  transform: scale(1.05); /* Slight zoom effect on hover */
}

/* Video Section */
.video-container {
  text-align: center;
  margin-top: 30px;
  padding: 20px;
  background: #3a3a3a; /* Medium grey */
  border-radius: 10px;
  box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.3); /* Golden shadow */
  transition: transform 0.3s ease;
}

.video-container:hover {
  transform: scale(1.05);
}

.video-container iframe {
  max-width: 100%;
  height: 400px;
  border-radius: 10px;
  border: 5px solid #ffd700; /* Golden border */
}

/* Responsive Design */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .images img {
    max-width: 100%; /* Ensures the image fits the container width on smaller screens */
  }

  .video-container iframe {
    height: 250px;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2rem;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }
}
}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Porsche Panamera Guide</h1>

    <!-- Overview Section -->
    <div class="card">
      <h2>Overview</h2>
      <p>The Porsche Panamera is a luxury sports sedan that combines performance, elegance, and cutting-edge technology. Known for its dynamic driving experience and opulent interior, the Panamera is a top choice for those who demand the very best in automotive excellence.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Single Image Section -->
    <div class="images">
      <img src="https://img.indianautosblog.com/2009/02/porsche_panamera_indian_autos_blog_30.jpg" alt="Porsche Panamera">
    </div>

    <!-- Key Features Section -->
    <div class="card">
      <h2>Key Features</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Luxurious Interior:</strong> Premium leather seats with elegant accents, complemented by ambient lighting for a refined atmosphere.</li>
        <li><strong>Advanced Technology:</strong> Features the latest Porsche Communication Management (PCM) system, digital instrument cluster, and voice control.</li>
        <li><strong>Comfort:</strong> Equipped with massaging seats, four-zone climate control, and a panoramic sunroof.</li>
        <li><strong>Performance:</strong> Offers a range of powerful engines, including hybrid options, for a thrilling driving experience.</li>
        <li><strong>Safety:</strong> Comprehensive safety features, including adaptive cruise control, lane-keeping assist, and autonomous driving capabilities.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Performance Section -->
    <div class="card">
      <h2>Performance</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Engine Options:</strong> Range includes a 2.9-liter V6, 4.0-liter V8, and a plug-in hybrid variant.</li>
        <li><strong>Power Output:</strong> Up to 690 horsepower in the Turbo S E-Hybrid variant.</li>
        <li><strong>Transmission:</strong> 8-speed automatic with all-wheel drive.</li>
        <li><strong>Acceleration:</strong> 0-60 mph in as little as 3.0 seconds (Turbo S E-Hybrid variant).</li>
        <li><strong>Top Speed:</strong> Electronically limited to 196 mph (315 km/h), with higher limits available on certain models.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Video Section -->
    <div class="video-container">
      <h2>Learn More About the Porsche Panamera</h2>
      <iframe
        width="560"
        height="400"
        src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/-QfRAwg3gkM" <!-- Replace with a relevant Porsche Panamera video -->
        title="YouTube video player"
        frameborder="0"
        allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
        allowfullscreen
      ></iframe>
    </div>

    <!-- Technology Section -->
    <div class="card">
      <h2>Technology</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Porsche Communication Management (PCM):</strong> Features a 12.3-inch touchscreen, gesture control, and natural language voice commands.</li>
        <li><strong>Digital Instrument Cluster:</strong> Fully customizable for a modern and cohesive look.</li>
        <li><strong>Driver Assistance:</strong> Includes adaptive cruise control, lane-keeping assist, and traffic jam assist.</li>
        <li><strong>Comfort Features:</strong> Equipped with massaging seats, advanced climate control, and ambient lighting with customizable colors.</li>
        <li><strong>Safety:</strong> Comprehensive safety features, including airbags, ABS, and stability control.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>